text: Tambet Pikkor (born 17 April 1980) is an Estonian ski jumper. He competed at the 1998 Winter Olympics, the 2002 Winter Olympics, and the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male ski jumpers Category:Estonian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Estonia Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Estonia Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn
